title: A PC Bull Market Could Be Coming, but Will AMD or Intel's Stock Be the Bigger Winner?
description: Advanced Micro Devices (NASDAQ: AMD) and Intel (NASDAQ: INTC) are huge players in the consumer electronics market, but does one provide better potential returns for investors?
